:

*Govorio je da će otići.* (He was saying that he was going to leave.)
*Gošća je došla da se pozdravi.* (The guest came to say goodbye.)
*Sutra ću otići u grad.* (Tomorrow I'm going to the city.)
*Gozba je trajala do kasno u noć.* (The feast lasted until late at night.)
*Gospodin je izašao da prošeta.* (The gentleman went out for a walk.)